<br />Was very limited and very hard to find when you can find it.  Its very expenisive.  So was thinking about making my own.  Would it be possible and work to use 2 NES 60-to-72 pins converter together to act as a spacer?  I made up a Picture to show what I want to do is it possible?  My toughts would be it would cost be only about $10-$20 USD to make this my self.
<br />
<br />Nes game genie&gt;"72 pin Female to 60 pin male converter (Store Bought)" &gt; "60 pin Female to 72 male converter (Homemade)" &gt;Nes TopLoader
<br /><img src="http://i29.tinypic.com/hwa9p0.jpg" alt="Image" />

		

